UnicodeStrings.StringIdContent: Put your skill and wit to the test against up to 7 opponents. Plays Slayer and a smattering of objective games.
Join alone or as a party for a 2 team game of up to 8 players. Plays primarily CTF and other objective games.
Go head to head against a single opponent of comparable skill in straight up Slayer games.
Join alone or as a party and be matched into a 2 team game of up to 16 players. Plays primarily objective games.
Join as a party of 3-4 Clan members to challenge another Clan for glory and honor! Plays the Team Skirmish playlist games.
Join as a party of 6-8 Clan members and face an enemy clan in an ultimate battle royale! Uses the Big Team Battle games.
Practice games from the team playlists unranked. Guests are allowed and any size party can join.
Join alone or as a party for a 2 team game of Slayer with up to 8 players.
Practice games from the Rumble Pit playlist unranked. Guests are allowed and any size party can join.
